caption.p: Molecular models of astragaloside II and neocryptotanshinone II binding to their predicted protein targets. ALB protein showed interaction with the astragaloside II molecule. The proteins CYP1A1, CYP1A2, APOA1, TNF, IL-6, and NFKB1 showed interactions with the neocryptotanshinone II molecule. Off-white diagrams represent receptors (target proteins), and pink diagrams represent ligands (compounds).
